import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Header from './components/common/heading/Header'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
      <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route />
      </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
